samples <- list.files("data/") 
samples <- samples[grep(pattern = "0.025_salmon", x = samples)]


file <- paste0("data/", samples[1], "/", "quant.sf")
quant <- read.csv(file, sep = "\t", header = T)
length <- quant$Length

#distribution of lengths
